| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1333 — Recovery Inhibition (nitrogen)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9d5454c2-003a-5a5f-83d1-2cdc528ec5d2"
